# Workspace Guidelines & Rules

All actions and commands in this workspace must adhere to the global rule definitions in:
`C:\Users\Admin\.gemini\GEMINI.md`

## Enforced Playbooks & Skills
Before running commands or modifying files, you MUST cross-reference the corresponding skill guidelines in the local library:
`C:\Users\Admin\.gemini\config\plugins\antigravity-awesome-skills\skills`

Specifically:
- Clarify ambiguous requirements first: `ask-questions-if-underspecified`
- Planning before coding: `planning-with-files` / `concise-planning`
- Coding & bugs: `test-driven-development` & `systematic-debugging`
- Commit naming: `git-pushing`
